\left||a\right\|^{2} =  a^{T}a
a^{T}b = \cos \theta \left ||a\right|\left||b\right|
p=\hat{x}a = \frac{\cos \theta \left ||a\right|\left||b\right|}{\left||a\right\|^{2}}a
